other_tests.findings: Numerous leukocytes and no organisms, including no mycobacteria. Pathological examination showed granulomas with necrosis resembling caseation consistent with active tuberculosis.
other_tests.changes_over_time: The supraclavicular abscess resolved after antibiotic treatment.

other_tests.findings: Mutations associated with multidrug resistance were detected; high-level resistance to protease inhibitors and nucleoside reverse-transcriptase inhibitors.
